I could see him again.

238
00:14:10,326 --> 00:14:12,660
Me too.

239
00:14:12,693 --> 00:14:16,593
I still need to thank him for
the painting, so, what do you
say we keep looking?

240
00:14:16,626 --> 00:14:17,260
Mhm!

241
00:14:17,293 --> 00:14:18,460
Let's go!

242
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:21,826
Hey, is that Luna?

243
00:14:28,926 --> 00:14:29,526
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Luna!</i>

244
00:14:29,593 --> 00:14:31,626
Huh? Oh, hi, girls!

245
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:33,960
What are you doing all
the way out here?

246
00:14:33,993 --> 00:14:38,260
Well... I sense an evil aura
emanating from this place.

247
00:14:38,293 --> 00:14:39,493
[gasps]

248
00:14:50,026 --> 00:14:52,260
How is my portrait coming along?

249
00:14:52,293 --> 00:14:53,993
Can I see it, please?

250
00:14:54,026 --> 00:14:57,160
Yeah okay...

251
00:14:59,126 --> 00:15:03,333
You know, I gotta say, I'm proud
of it. I think it captures you
well.

252
00:15:03,333 --> 00:15:06,333
Oh my, is that
supposed to be me?

253
00:15:06,333 --> 00:15:08,633
It doesn't look
anything like me.

254
00:15:08,666 --> 00:15:10,033
Huh?

255
00:15:10,100 --> 00:15:12,700
