one more time:

266
00:15:41,666 --> 00:15:45,700
My eyes are prettier than
that, aren't they?

267
00:15:45,766 --> 00:15:50,133
Sorry, but I didn't
agree to come here&
to paint lies for you.

268
00:15:50,166 --> 00:15:54,500
