<i>who'll wind up in trouble.</i>

280
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,606
[groan]

281
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:42,306
Look at that&! So perfect...

282
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:45,106
You did an excellent job.

283
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:49,173
I don't feel well. Excuse me, I
think I need a little rest.

284
00:16:49,173 --> 00:16:51,206
Hold on, you can't go.

285
00:16:51,273 --> 00:16:55,840
See, We're not done here.
There's one more important thing
I still need from you.

286
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:01,713
[gasp]

287
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:02,946
Who are you!?

288
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,846
Mr. Kamoi!

289
00:17:04,846 --> 00:17:08,380
Now then, let's take a look at
your Dream Mirror, shall we?

290
00:17:08,446 --> 00:17:12,180
<i>(Sailor Moon)</i>
<i>Hold it right there!</i>

291
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:18,280
How dare you deceive a poor, but
pure and sincere artist who's
trying to make an honest living!

292
00:17:18,313 --> 00:17:19,846
That is unforgivable!

293
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,346
We're the Pretty Guardians...

294
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:26,513
...who fight for love
and for justice!

295
00:17:26,546 --> 00:17:29,346
I am Sailor Moon!

296
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:32,513
And I am Sailor Chibi Moon!

297
00:17:32,546 --> 00:17:35,113
And in the name of the Moon,

298
00:17:35,146 --> 00:17:37,046
‐we'll punish you!
‐we'll punish you!

299
00:17:37,113 --> 00:17:39,680
Oh my, if it isn't
the uneven duo.

300
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,513
