302
00:17:46,213 --> 00:17:48,780
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>What?! She only called us that</i>
<i>'cause you're such a shrimp!</i>

303
00:17:48,813 --> 00:17:50,513
<i>(Sailor Chibi Moon)</i>
<i>I can't help that,</i>
<i>I'm still a kid.</i>

304
00:17:50,513 --> 00:17:51,680
Excuse me!

305
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,346
‐Yeah?
‐Yeah?

306
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:55,880
By chance, do the two of you
like playing billiards?

307
00:17:55,946 --> 00:17:56,513
‐Huh?
‐Huh?

308
00:17:56,580 --> 00:17:58,646
What are billiards again?

309
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,353
The one with sticks and balls?

310
00:18:00,353 --> 00:18:02,720
You are correct! Orb Shot!

311
00:18:02,786 --> 00:18:03,886
[screams]

312
00:18:03,953 --> 00:18:05,486
[grunts]

313
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:08,186
[scream]

314
00:18:11,486 --> 00:18:15,186
