315
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:17,553
It's not the Golden Mirror.
In fact, it's not even a
beautiful dream...!

316
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:22,320
That's not true! Mr. Kamoi
definitely does have a
beautiful dream!

317
00:18:22,353 --> 00:18:24,186
You're just too blind to see it!

318
00:18:24,186 --> 00:18:28,020
Whatever, I have no use
for his filthy mirror.

319
00:18:28,020 --> 00:18:32,520
Flower Lemures... Ms. Toge‐Toge,
