338
00:19:41,693 --> 00:19:48,460
Moon Gorgeous Meditation!

339
00:19:59,326 --> 00:20:05,800
But I didn't even do
anything... Stage Out, toge!

340
00:20:08,800 --> 00:20:15,500
You may have won today, but it
won't be like this next time.

341
00:20:16,733 --> 00:20:20,333
Well, the enemy's gone, so we
can return the Dream Mirror.

342
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:23,066
[sad sigh]

343
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:28,833
It'll be okay. Once he wakes
up, Mr. Kamoi will remember
his beautiful dream again.

344
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:32,133
[happy gasp]

345
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:35,466
[groans]

346
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,466
<i>(Chibi Moo)</i>
<i>Mr. Kamoi..</i>

347
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:40,066
Are you alright?!

348
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:44,300
You must be the people
who saved my life.

349
00:20:44,333 --> 00:20:47,433
<i>I feel like I was trapped</i>
<i>in a really long dream.</i>

350
00:20:47,466 --> 00:20:50,633
Were you dreaming of being rich?

351
00:20:50,633 --> 00:20:54,933
No. I was tempted by all that
wealth, but it wasn't worth it.

352
00:20:54,966 --> 00:20:58,466
I learned I can't put a price
on my artistic integrity.

353
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,273
